parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The intermittent stalling of the vehicle can cause a loss of control, leading to accidents and injuries, while the failure of fuses can lead to a range of electrical system malfunctions, affecting vehicle safety and performance.

fuses fail
loss of control
accidents

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Clutch slipping can cause the vehicle to lose power, leading to reduced acceleration, difficulty merging, and increased risk of stalling, which can increase the risk of accidents.
symptoms: The clutch pedal feels soft or spongy
the vehicle hesitates or stumbles when accelerating
the engine RPMs increase without a corresponding increase in speed
the vehicle loses power or speed when shifting gears.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Transmission Shuddering and Loss of Gear
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Transmission shuddering and loss of gear can cause the vehicle to lose power, leading to reduced acceleration, difficulty merging, and increased risk of stalling, which can increase the risk of accidents.
symptoms: The transmission shudders or vibrates
the vehicle hesitates or stumbles when shifting gears
the gear shifts are rough or abrupt
the vehicle jumps out of gear
the vehicle is unable to maintain a steady speed.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Gear Shift Lever Rubber Boot Failure
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Failure of the gear shift lever rubber boot can cause the gear shift lever to become stuck or difficult to operate, leading to reduced control over the vehicle and increased risk of accidents.
symptoms: The gear shift lever is difficult to move or becomes stuck
the gear shift lever is loose or wobbly
the gear shift lever rubber boot is cracked or broken.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: A faulty seat belt can fail to restrain the passenger in the event of sudden stops or accidents, increasing the risk of injury or fatality.
symptoms: The seat belt fails to tighten
the seat belt fits loosely around the passenger
the seat belt does not latch or unlatch properly
the seat belt is stuck in a retracted position
the seat belt warning light is illuminated.
